+    // by Media3): set on a FOLDER to control how its CHILDREN render.
+    // 1 = list, 2 = grid (cover tiles), 3 = category list (tinted icons),
+    // 4 = category grid. Status badges (checkmark/progress/download) overlay
+    // grid tiles too, so grids keep all the indicators.
+    private val STYLE_LIST = 1
+    private val STYLE_GRID = 2
+    private val STYLE_CATEGORY_LIST = 3
